---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import atkImage from "./public/img/atk.webp";
import dcdImage from "./public/img/dcd.webp";
import itmvImage from "./public/img/itmv.webp";

---
<section id="section 4 mt-2">
  <div class="projectcards">
    
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center h-screen w-full bg-cover sticky top-20">
        <div class="w-4/5 lg:w-2/5 mx-auto p-8 bg-[var(--box-color)]">
            <h5 class="pb-6 text-4xl uppercase"><strong>Plastic Change</strong></h5>
            <h6>Plastic Change is a Danish organization dedicated to fighting for a world free from plastic pollution.<br><br>
                 They needed a digital one-page fundraising campaign to encourage individuals to contribute through either a one-time donation or a monthly membership.<br><br>
                 My primary focus was on project management, the Figma design process, handling coding tasks, and managing routine work.
            </h6>
        </div>
        <div class="w-4/5">
            <a href="https://plasticchange17.netlify.app/" target="_blank">
                <img src="../img/plasticchange.webp" alt="Landingpage for I Tråd Med Verden" class="transition-all duration-300 filter grayscale hover:filter-none"/>
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="flex flex-col items-center h-screen w-full bg-cover sticky top-20">
        <div class="w-4/5 lg:w-2/5 mx-auto p-8 bg-[var(--box-color)]">
            <h5 class="pb-6 text-4xl uppercase"><strong>Digital cleanup day</strong></h5><!-- kom mere tekst på så man ikke kan se det andet proect i baggrunden -->
            <h6 class="pb-20">Digital Cleanup Day was a collaborative group project where we developed a concept for a Danish version of digitalcleanupday.org.<br><br>
                 I primarily focused on the Figma design process. We also used Astro, Tailwind CSS, and Alpine.js to bring our vision to life.
            </h6>
        </div>
        <div class="w-4/5">
            <a href="https://digitalskraldedaggr4.netlify.app" target="_blank">
                <img src="../img/dcd.webp" alt="Landingpage for Digital Cleanup Day" class="transition-all duration-300 filter grayscale hover:filter-none"/>
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center h-screen w-full bg-cover sticky top-20">
        <div class="w-4/5 lg:w-2/5 mx-auto p-8 bg-[var(--box-color)]">
            <h5 class="pb-6 text-4xl uppercase"><strong>Arbejdernes Tennisklub</strong></h5>
            <h6>This project was a second-semester exam assignment where<!-- , as a group,  --> we collaborated with Arbejdernes Tennisklub(ATK) to redesign their website.<br><br>
                 The goal was to simplify the site and make it more user-friendly<!-- , with clearer information, --> aiming to strengthen the community and increase member engagement.<br><br>
                 My focus was on the Figma design process and developing content for social media.
            </h6>
        </div>
        <div class="w-4/5">
            <a href="https://atk-website.netlify.app/" target="_blank">
                <img src="../img/atk.webp" alt="Landingpage for Arbejdernes Tennisklub" class="transition-all duration-300 filter grayscale hover:filter-none"/>
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center h-screen w-full bg-cover sticky top-20">
        <div class="w-4/5 lg:w-2/5 mx-auto p-8 bg-[var(--box-color)]">
            <h5 class="pb-6 text-4xl uppercase"><strong>I Tråd Med Verden</strong></h5>
            <h6>
                For I Tråd Med Verden (ITMV), the task was to develop a digital solution with a web feature and create content for both the website and social media.<br><br>
                The goal was to generate engagement and increase conversions from both private donors and businesses, with a specific focus on targeting women in corporate positions who could advocate for our cause within their organizations.<br><br>
                My focus was primarily on the Figma design phase, handling coding tasks and managing routine work.
            </h6>
        </div>
        <div class="w-4/5">
            <a href="https://itmv20.netlify.app" target="_blank">
                <img src="../img/itmv.webp" alt="Landingpage for I Tråd Med Verden" class="transition-all duration-300 filter grayscale hover:filter-none"/>
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>